
# @host = http://localhost:8080
@host = http://localhost:9001

### Create Task
POST {{host}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taskName": "Wasje draaien",
  "dueDate": "2026-06-12"
}

### Complete Task
PUT {{host}}/tasks/complete/5847f645-2f48-4c75-a957-07e6405105ec


### Find Tasks
GET {{host}}/tasks


### Find completed Tasks
GET {{host}}/tasks/complete